CRUSH IT WORKOUT🥵 Save it for later! 

Let your actions match your intentions.If you truly want something, set a plan and put in the work to achieve it. Get serious about your goals, believe in yourself and make it happen!!💫 

METHOD ➡️ 12-15 reps per side | 4 sets | 30 secs rest 

Tag your friends & go crush it! ⤵️ @gymshark

Sippin on @womensbest 

#absworkout #hiitworkout #coreworkout

NEXEL LEVEL LEGS😳🔥 Save it for later!

METHOD ➡️ 12-15 reps per side | 4 sets | 30 secs rest 

Tag your friends & go crush it! ⤵️ @gymshark
